OL,3,CGlasgow Central remains closed after
OL,4,Chuge fire nearby
OL,6,FGlasgow Central Station will remain
OL,7,Fclosed for the rest of the week,
OL,8,Ffollowing a huge fire at a vape shop
OL,9,Fnext to Scotland's busiest station.
OL,11,FNetwork Rail said it will not be
OL,12,Fpossible to reopen the high-level part
OL,13,Fof the station because of the
OL,14,Finstability of the Union Corner site's
OL,15,Ffacade, much of which collapsed during
OL,16,Fthe blaze.
OL,18,FHowever, the low-level part of Glasgow
OL,19,FCentral will open on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
