PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773245483
OL,3,CGlasgow Central remains closed after
OL,4,Chuge fire nearby
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, further work is
OL,7,Frequired to ensure the high-level
OL,8,Fstation is safe for trains to operate.
OL,9,FOur priority is to make sure that we
OL,10,Fcan reopen Glasgow Central as soon as
OL,11,Fit is safe to do so and we will
OL,12,Fcontinue to work with emergency
OL,13,Fservices, the local council and our
OL,14,Ftrain operators to restore services.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
