OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773245483
OL,3,CGlasgow Central remains closed after
OL,4,Chuge fire nearby
OL,6,F"We want to reassure passengers that
OL,7,Fwe are doing everything we can to open
OL,8,Fthe high-level station, but we must
OL,9,Fenable the emergency services and
OL,10,FGlasgow City Council to complete their
OL,11,Fcritical work to secure the Union
OL,12,FCorner site and make it safe."
OL,14,FDavid Ross, ScotRail's chief operating
OL,15,Fofficer, said: "We know this closure
OL,16,Fis causing significant disruption for
OL,17,Four customers, and we're very sorry
OL,18,Ffor the impact it is having on
OL,19,Fjourneys."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@^O]wD@POU{D@JO]
