OL,3,CGlasgow Central remains closed after
OL,4,Chuge fire nearby
OL,6,FNo trains have been running to or from
OL,7,FCentral Station's high level on Monday
OL,8,For Tuesday, with trains passing
OL,9,Fthrough the lower level without
OL,10,Fstopping.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FFirst Minister John Swinney paid
OL,18,Ftribute to firefighters and other
OL,19,Femergency services who attended the
OL,20,Fscene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
