OL,3,CGlasgow Central remains closed after
OL,4,Chuge fire nearby
OL,6,FMr Swinney added: "It's still a very
OL,7,Flive site, that is still under not
OL,8,Fjust investigation, but under
OL,9,Fstabilisation adjacent to Glasgow
OL,10,FCentral.
OL,12,F"There's a building adjacent to the
OL,13,FGordon Street entrance which is
OL,14,Fextremely vulnerable, so the
OL,15,Freassurance I would give is that will
OL,16,Fbe undertaken as quickly as we
OL,17,Fpossibly can do, but I can't give a
OL,18,Fdefinitive timescale on that."
