OL,3,CGlasgow Central remains closed after
OL,4,Chuge fire nearby
OL,6,FA B-listed Victorian building, home to
OL,7,Fseveral businesses, was engulfed in
OL,8,Fthe blaze.
OL,10,FTens of thousands of pounds have been
OL,11,Fraised on crowdfunding platform
OL,12,FGoFundMe to support six businesses
OL,13,Fwhich lost their premises.
OL,15,FThe businesses include a hairdressing
OL,16,Fsalon run by Joe Diaz, who fled the
OL,17,Fbuilding when the fire began to take
OL,18,Fhold on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
