OL,3,CGlasgow Central remains closed after
OL,4,Chuge fire nearby
OL,6,FHe said that his partner encountered
OL,7,F"really heavy, dark smoke" as they
OL,8,Ffled the scene.
OL,10,F"We just got our client and said,
OL,11,Flet's just run and get out of here as
OL,12,Fsoon as we can", Diaz added.
OL,14,FA passer-by, Lamin Kongira, tried to
OL,15,Fextinguish the blaze in a vape shop on
OL,16,FSunday, but was forced back by an
OL,17,F"explosion" from within the premises.
OL,19,FHe described hearing another more
OL,20,Fpowerful blast shortly afterwards.
